data.title: 6 Serviss St, South River, NJ 08882
data.meta_description: Zillow has 50 photos of this $495,000 3 beds, 3 baths, 3,170 Square Feet single family home located at 6 Serviss St, South River, NJ 08882 built in 1900. MLS #2500953R.
data.text: This charming home, located in the heart of South River, is conveniently close to stores, restaurants, and an NYC bus stop. Offering 3,170 sq ft of living space, the house includes a spacious living room, a study room, and several bonus rooms. It features three generously-sized bedrooms and three bathrooms. The first floor has an exterior door, while upstairs boasts its own entrance to a porch. Additionally, the property includes two large garages and sits on an oversized lot, providing ample space and convenience.
